text: 2014–15 Syed Mushtaq Ali Trophy was the sixth edition of the Syed Mushtaq Ali Trophy competition, an Indian domestic team only Twenty20 cricket tournament in India. It was contested by 27 teams. ==Format== The teams were divided into five zonal groups: Central, East, North, South and West.
